    "summary": "Specialities: Investment Management, Sales-Trading, Asset Management Sales & Business Development\n\nRuurd Haan is founder of RWH Investment Advisors. He has a degree in financial economics from the university of Groningen. He has followed financial markets on a daily basis since 1987 and has worked in the industry since 1995. Ruurd started his career as a quant analist and strategist for ING Group and continued as investment manager and strategist for the Unilever and Philips pension funds. Ruurd became manager of the sales-trading desk of ING Private Wealth & Asset Management in 2005. He was an advisor to the Investment Committee of ING Pension Fund from 2006-2009. He founded his own investment consultancy firm RWH Investment Advisors in 2010. Ruurd Haan connects boutique (alternative) asset managers to Dutch/Benelux institutional investors.\n\nCurrently he successfully works together with the following managers:\n- Luxcara (Hamburg): Core Renewable Energy Infrastructure (Europe)\n- Leadenhall Capital Partners (London): Insurance-Linked Investments\n- SUSI Partners (Zurich): Value-add Renewable Energy Infrastructure (Global)\n- Tulp Hypotheken (Utrecht): Dutch Mortgages\n- Fulcrum Asset Management (London): Global Macro Discretionary & Systematic Strategies",
